## Limitations

This report is based on publicly available information and may not cover all aspects of police investigations, particularly those that are confidential or vary significantly by jurisdiction. Additionally, the dynamic nature of law enforcement practices means that procedures can evolve, and this report may not reflect the most current methods used by police agencies.